com.developmentontheedge.beans

Class DynamicPropertySetAsMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.developmentontheedge.beans.AbstractDynamicPropertySet
      • com.developmentontheedge.beans.DynamicPropertySetAsMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicPropertySet, PropertyChangeObservable, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<DynamicProperty>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Preferences

    public class DynamicPropertySetAsMap
extends AbstractDynamicPropertySet
    Implementation of DynamicPropertySet as map. By default TreeMap is used. String comparator is used to sort properties by name in the map.
    See Also:
    TreeMap, Serialized Form
